  <p class="about_us_text">
    The Startup Network aims to connect you with your future startup cofounder.
  </p>
  <p class="about_us_text">
    It is a social networking site built specifically for HBS students, by an HBS student. It is designed to allow users to share their interests and passions, and to market their skills, experiences, and ideas to other members of the community.
  </p>
  <p class="about_us_text">
    Best of luck!
  </p>
  <p style="font-size:12px; font-weight:normal; margin-top: 50px;">
    P.S. This is very much still a work in progress. In the coming days/weeks I'm hoping to roll out new features and functionality like being able to create and contribute ideas, leave comments on them, and update your profile here using LinkedIn. Let me know what features you think are useful!
  </p>

