      <h2>{</h2>
      <p>
        Hi, my name is Eu-wen and I built this site.
      </p>
      <p>
        I built this because its hard to find the right startup cofounder, and it is impossible to meet every one of you awesome 899 HBS students whom I'll be starting with this fall.
      </p>
      <p>
        The idea for The Startup Network was born when I came across the spreadsheet of HBS students interested in entrepreneurship on Facebook. I loved the initiative, but thought a spreadsheet to be a poor tool to connect wannabe entrepreneurs to each other.
      </p>
      <p>
        I thought I could do a better job, so I built this. I really hope that you like it, that you will use it, and most importantly, that it will spark connections that result in meaningful relationships when we come together on campus this fall.
      </p>
